== Order of install ==

Install Apache1

    See docs/INSTALL.apache-perl

Install OpenSSL

Install Postgresql

    postgresql
    postgresql-server
    postgresql-devel

Create config

    $ cp /usr/share/pgsql/pg_hba.conf.sample /var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_hba.conf
    # now, edit the settings as in INSTALL

